{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_04_01",
  "title": "伊吹渚 1話 小悪魔といえば？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、すみません\nわざわざお時間を取ってもらって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I'm sorry for\ntaking your time like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "これくらい気にしないでくれ\nそれで、相談があるって聞いたけど、どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't worry about it.\nSo‚ you mentioned you have something to discuss. What's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、私も……\nユニットを組ませてもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I…\nCould I have a special team too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりだな。私「も」ってことは……\n雫と天動さんのユニットを見てそう思ったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's quite sudden. The \"too\" implies…\nDid you get the idea after seeing Shizuku and Tendo's team?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。でも、雫ちゃんと瑠依ちゃんのライブを見て\nいいなと思ったから、というよりは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ but it's not just that.\nAfter seeing Shizuku-chan and Rui-chan's live performance‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "結果としてのライブより、そこに至るまで二人が\n悩んでぶつかって、成長したことに刺激を受けたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized it's not about the end result of the live but the\njourney of two people struggling and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん月ストの活動を\n中途半端にするつもりはありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "growing together that inspired me.\nOf course‚ I have no intention of doing things half-heartedly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "どんどん一体感が出て\n練習もライブも楽しくなってますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for Moon Tempest. As we become more cohesive‚\nboth practice and live performances become more enjoyable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、これからグループとしてもっと\n成長していくには……個人の成長も必要なのかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ I believe that for our group to grow even more‚\nindividual growth is essential.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "それで、誰かとユニットを組めば、月ストとはまた違う\n刺激を受けて成長につながるかも……って思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I thought that by forming a team with someone‚\nI could gain different types of inspiration‚ which would lead to personal growth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら、私にも相手にも……それに何より\n月ストにいい影響があるんじゃないかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moreover‚ it might have a positive\nimpact on Moon Tempest as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。最初は何事かと思ったけど\nどうしたら成長出来るか、ちゃんと考えてる訳か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I was a bit surprised at first‚\nbut you've obviously put some thought into this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、もし誰とでもユニットを組めるとしたら\n誰と組んでみたいんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ if you could form a team with anyone‚\nwho would you choose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "まず最初に浮かぶのは琴乃ちゃんなんですけど\nいつも一緒にいますから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ the first person who comes to mind is\nKotono-chan since we're always together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "今回で言えば、他の人の方がいいかもしれません……\n例えば、千紗ちゃんはどうでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But for this time‚ maybe it's better if it's someone else…\nHow about Chisa-chan‚ for example?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "穏やかなユニットになりそうだな。刺激となると……\n月ストとサニピ以外の誰かがいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like it would be a calm team. In terms of stimulation…\nMaybe someone other than Moon Tempest or Sunny Peace would be better?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、確かに……そうかもしれないですね\nとなると、トリエルかリズノワのみんなかー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you have a point… that might be true.\nIn that case‚ it could be TRINITYAiLE or LizNoir…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、具体的に考えると意外に難しいですねー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ when you think about it in detail‚ it's surprisingly difficult…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "雫と天動さんのユニットのどこに刺激を受けたのか\nもう少し具体的に掘り下げてみたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where exactly did you find inspiration from Shizuku and Rui's team?\nHow about digging a bit deeper into that for a more specific idea?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "具体的に……あ、そうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A bit more specific… oh‚ I remember.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "私、雫ちゃんが瑠依ちゃんにはっきり意見を伝えたって\n聞いた時に、凄くじーんときたんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I heard that Shizuku-chan clearly expressed\nher opinion to Rui-chan‚ I was deeply moved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "大人しい雫ちゃんが、まさかあの瑠依ちゃんに……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ the quiet Shizuku-chan‚ boldly expressing her thoughts to Rui-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。それなら、雫にとっての天動さんのように\nなかなか意見を言い辛い相手はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So‚ how about partnering with someone\nlike how Shizuku does with Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "相手に伝える意見を深く考える中で\n渚自身の価値観や信念にも気付けるかもしれないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone who finds it hard to express their opinions‚ just like Shizuku‚\ncould help you discover your own values and beliefs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
